text: Myfanwy Warhurst (born May 29, 1973) is an Australian radio announcer and television personality who is best known for her work on the Triple J radio stations and being Australia’s commentator for the Eurovision Song Contest alongside Joey Creasey. She also provides the voice for Aunt Trixie and Indy’s Mum on the Australian animated series Bluey.
